# WebRTC Infrastructure — Implementation Walkthrough

> ✅ **Build Status**: TypeScript compiles cleanly with zero errors (`tsc --noEmit` and `tsc` both pass)

---

## Overview

This implementation translates the 4-part architecture specification into production-grade TypeScript code within the existing Fastify backend. Every component from the spec has been implemented as a separate, focused module.

